      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model adopted for titanium alloy components consistent with sub-yield loading regime of ASTM F1717. Contact formulation at screw-rod interface validated against published literature."
    },
