      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single load condition (compression-bending at standard F1717 geometry) only. Variation in load angle or magnitude not explored, limiting coverage of the boundary condition space. This factor does not meet the required level."
